Job Description – P2SP Engineer (Backend) 

We are looking for a peer-to-peer engineer to join our backend team working on our peer-to-peer module and algorithms. You will design and implement peer-to-peer distributed systems features, with the goal of making it more efficient on all platforms. You will help us to create cutting edge solutions for multi-CDN, to expand our successful solutions into markets.

我們正在尋找peer-to-peer工程師加入後端團隊一起合作開發peer-to-peer模組與演算法.你將有機會對peer-to-peer分散式系統進行功能設計與實作, 目標是提升此技術在平台的正確與可靠度.你將幫助mlytics將獨家技術與Multi CDN整合,最終有助於將此解決方案推廣到市場幫助公司成長.

[Responsibilities]:
>Design, implement and test software components;
>Develop client-side SDK that integrated with desktop browser and mobile native App;
>Design peer-to-peer algorithms for real-world distributed system;
>Use WebRTC protocol to delivery video streaming content to the users around the world.

>對軟體元件進行設計, 實作與測試;
>對桌面瀏覽器與移動裝置App研發用戶端SDK;
>設計peer-to-peer演算法並將其運行於真實世界的分散系統;
>使用WebRTC協定將影像串流內容地送到設計各地的使用者.

[Requirements]
>BA/BS in Computer Science or equivalent experience;
>3+ years professional experience as a developer/engineer;
>Knowledge of one or more mainstream programming languages (Typescript);
>Solid understanding of RESTful APIs and service security;
>Working knowledge of SQL and relational databases such as PostgreSQL or MySQL;
>Strong interpersonal and communication skills with a bias towards action
>Will be a plus - Experience with WebRTC protocol. 

>具備大學或大學電腦科學以上學歷, 或具備相關工作經驗;
>三年以上軟體開發經驗;
>熟悉只少一個編程語言(Javascript, Typescript, Golang);
>熟悉RESTful API與後端服務安全;
>具備關連式資料庫實際操作與開發經驗, 例如PostgreSQL或MySQL;
>重視溝通與團隊合作;
>加分條件- 曾經有WebRTC相關經歷.
